To be honest with you,
it's been tough for me too.

540
00:41:06,330 --> 00:41:08,720
At least I'm much
better off than Yun-Shil.

541
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,730
At least I have you.

542
00:41:13,790 --> 00:41:16,780
You're such a good husband.

543
00:41:23,300 --> 00:41:24,760
What was that about?

544
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:27,690
I only gave you a nudge.

545
00:41:27,690 --> 00:41:30,520
You're overreacting.

546
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:34,560
I'm too busy with work.

547
00:41:34,560 --> 00:41:36,490
I want to sleep.

548
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:40,690
How can you do this to me?

549
00:41:40,690 --> 00:41:43,450
You've never done this to me before!

550
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:46,680
You're acting strange.

551
00:41:46,680 --> 00:41:49,680
Let's just sleep. I'm tired.

552
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:56,730
Are you cheating on me?

553
00:41:56,730 --> 00:41:58,770
Cheating on you?

554
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:05,590
Why are you accusing
me all of a sudden?

555
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:13,440
Did those women with botox on their brains tell you that I'm cheating?

556
00:42:15,670 --> 00:42:18,340
Is that what you guys talk about?

557
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:22,340
Why do you want to hang out
with those losers?

558
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:23,680
Don't you have anything better to do?

559
00:42:23,680 --> 00:42:25,400
What's wrong with you?

560
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,470
You don't know anything about them.

561
00:42:26,470 --> 00:42:27,650
Why are you dissing them
without a good reason?

562
00:42:27,650 --> 00:42:29,470
Without a good reason?

563
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:35,500
Do you want me to tell you why they're losers?

564
00:42:36,350 --> 00:42:39,730
Why are the three women with botox on their brains hanging out together?

565
00:42:40,590 --> 00:42:42,680
There's a woman who
wears used clothes...

566
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:45,320
...and refused to give birth in order
to raise someone else's kids.

567
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:47,320
Yet her husband cheated on her.

568
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:49,600
There must be another reason
why a poor woman like that is dead.

569
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:52,630
Do you just feel sorry for her?

570
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:55,740
Did it ever occur to you
that she may be incompetent?

571
00:42:55,740 --> 00:42:58,620
Why wear used clothes when
you have money to buy new ones?

572
00:42:58,620 --> 00:43:00,720
Why get an abortion when
you can be a good mother?

573
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:04,560
Why would her husband
cheat on her if she's attractive?

574
00:43:04,560 --> 00:43:08,690
Sacrifice? No, she's just incompetent!

575
00:43:08,690 --> 00:43:12,390
We have wrinkles on our
brains so we can think!

576
00:43:12,390 --> 00:43:14,310
Not to drive ourselves into fantasy!

577
00:43:14,310 --> 00:43:15,610
Understand?

578
00:43:15,610 --> 00:43:19,460
They can't make progress
because they think that's sacrifice!

579
00:43:19,460 --> 00:43:22,310
They're losers because
they think like that!

580
00:43:22,310 --> 00:43:24,330
How...how can you say that?

581
00:43:24,330 --> 00:43:25,760
Stop!

582
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:29,400
That's enough.

583
00:43:29,640 --> 00:43:31,790
I don't want to talk about it anymore.

584
00:43:32,680 --> 00:43:34,490
Good night!

585
00:43:39,310 --> 00:43:40,540
I'm tired.

586
00:43:57,350 --> 00:44:03,370
I never knew that's what
you thought about them.

587
00:44:04,370 --> 00:44:08,520
What are you talking about?

588
00:44:08,520 --> 00:44:10,590
Is that what you think about me too?

589
00:44:10,590 --> 00:44:12,690
I bring used clothes and
used furniture home too.

590
00:44:13,650 --> 00:44:15,730
I don't even think about
having a third child.

591
00:44:17,490 --> 00:44:20,340
Is that because I'm incompetent?

592
00:44:20,340 --> 00:44:24,490
If you cheat on me, does that mean
it's because I'm unattractive?

593
00:44:24,490 --> 00:44:25,790
If that scares you,
then you should try harder.

594
00:44:25,790 --> 00:44:28,790
Try harder! Make some progress!

595
00:44:28,790 --> 00:44:31,410
You're wrong!

596
00:44:31,410 --> 00:44:32,460
If we keep this up...

597
00:44:32,460 --> 00:44:34,670
...you'll look down on me and cheat on me like Yun-Shil's husband did.

598
00:44:34,670 --> 00:44:36,650
Then you'll blame it on me!

599
00:44:36,650 --> 00:44:37,560
No way!

600
00:44:37,560 --> 00:44:39,440
I won't let that happen!

601
00:44:39,440 --> 00:44:41,450
You should change the way you think!

602
00:44:42,510 --> 00:44:43,450
Don't laugh at me.

603
00:44:43,450 --> 00:44:44,780
I'm Gyung Guk-Hee.

604
00:44:44,780 --> 00:44:46,610
What about Gyung Guk-Hee?

605
00:44:46,610 --> 00:44:50,730
I'm Gyung Guk-Hee,
the woman you wanted to marry.

606
00:44:52,600 --> 00:44:53,790
I'm working hard to
make it through this life.

607
00:44:53,790 --> 00:44:55,480
You don't have a reason to diss me.

608
00:44:55,480 --> 00:44:56,630
The same goes for Yun-Shil.

609
00:44:56,630 --> 00:44:59,460
It's the white pants
who's wrong, not Yun-Shil.

610
00:45:00,370 --> 00:45:04,530
If she has been wronged,
then I will help her.

611
00:45:04,530 --> 00:45:06,550
I'll do whatever I can to bring justice.

612
00:45:08,400 --> 00:45:09,490
Mind your own business.

613
00:45:09,490 --> 00:45:10,790
Don't look down on me!

614
00:45:10,790 --> 00:45:12,560
Don't yell at me!

615
00:45:12,560 --> 00:45:13,590
- Are you on drugs or something?
- Stop!

616
00:45:13,590 --> 00:45:14,660
That's enough.

617
00:45:14,660 --> 00:45:16,680
I don't want to talk
about it anymore. Let's eat.

618
00:45:25,610 --> 00:45:27,780
Make sure you do that
camping exercise with Eun-Suk.

619
00:45:27,780 --> 00:45:29,440
He's been looking forward
to this for a long time.

620
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:30,740
Come home by 4.

621
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:35,770
Good morning.

622
00:45:36,710 --> 00:45:41,760
I'm here to bother you on a
peaceful Saturday morning.

623
00:45:42,530 --> 00:45:47,640
The thing is, they're verified my alibi.

624
00:45:49,360 --> 00:45:52,590
It was my friend, not I,
who went to Sokcho that night.

625
00:45:52,590 --> 00:45:57,590
I proved that I have
nothing to do with Sokcho.

626
00:46:02,330 --> 00:46:06,730
That is the reason why
I'd like to sue you for slandering.

627
00:46:10,320 --> 00:46:15,570
I hope you're loaded.

628
00:46:20,540 --> 00:46:22,370
Bye.

629
00:46:29,630 --> 00:46:31,400
Did you see that?

630
00:46:31,400 --> 00:46:34,450
Do you still think I'm looking
down on you for no reason?

631
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:37,300
Go and beg him.

632
00:46:37,300 --> 00:46:40,710
Beg him, and make sure he changes
his mind by the end of the week.

633
00:46:55,790 --> 00:46:57,480
Mom...

634
00:46:59,480 --> 00:47:01,370
Let's go.

635
00:47:03,350 --> 00:47:04,470
Hold on.

636
00:47:07,410 --> 00:47:10,390
Can we talk? Are you by yourself?

637
00:47:10,390 --> 00:47:12,650
I'm Yun-Shil.

638
00:47:18,470 --> 00:47:20,420
Hello?

639
00:47:21,590 --> 00:47:23,580
Yun-Shil?

640
00:47:23,580 --> 00:47:25,700
Are you really Yun-Shil?

641
00:47:25,710 --> 00:47:29,410
I don't believe you.

642
00:47:31,310 --> 00:47:33,730
I'm Yun-Shil, the one said...

643
00:47:33,730 --> 00:47:37,650
...being a good wife is
the hardest thing you can be.

644
00:47:39,730 --> 00:47:43,510
It's hard to be a good wife.

645
00:47:43,510 --> 00:47:45,560
That's the hardest thing you can be.

646
00:47:48,330 --> 00:47:50,350
Yun-Shil?

647
00:47:50,350 --> 00:47:51,750
Are you really Yun-Shil?

648
00:47:52,730 --> 00:47:54,580
Are you alive?

649
00:47:54,580 --> 00:47:56,560
Can you come over?

650
00:47:59,490 --> 00:48:00,730
Don't tell anyone.

651
00:48:00,730 --> 00:48:02,540
I'm in Sokcho.

652
00:48:07,310 --> 00:48:12,340
Tae-Ran, do you know what you
can never hide in this world?

653
00:48:12,340 --> 00:48:17,370
Sneezing, poverty,
ticklish, and....love?

654
00:48:18,470 --> 00:48:22,420
My friends tell me that
I look happy nowadays.

655
00:48:23,470 --> 00:48:27,380
My assistant asked me
if I won the lottery.

656
00:48:29,430 --> 00:48:31,570
Let's go somewhere for the weekend.

657
00:48:31,570 --> 00:48:33,500
One night two days.

658
00:48:33,500 --> 00:48:35,590
How about it?

659
00:48:35,590 --> 00:48:37,380
Aren't you tired?

660
00:48:37,380 --> 00:48:39,440
Don't you need a break
for the weekend?

661
00:48:40,620 --> 00:48:46,670
The best part about dating is
that you always feel rejuvenated.

662
00:48:46,670 --> 00:48:50,410
I'm energized to the max.

663
00:48:51,470 --> 00:48:53,650
Then, do you want to go to Sokcho instead of Yangpyeong?

664
00:48:53,650 --> 00:48:55,680
There are mountains and the beach.

665
00:48:55,680 --> 00:48:58,440
Okay! Sure thing!

666
00:48:58,440 --> 00:49:01,300
You don't have to prepare anything!

667
00:49:01,300 --> 00:49:05,440
I'll arrange everything
from the car to the place.

668
00:49:06,310 --> 00:49:07,380
That's great!

669
00:49:07,380 --> 00:49:09,480
I needed a man like you.

670
00:49:10,410 --> 00:49:12,340
See you soon.

671
00:49:19,360 --> 00:49:21,450
If Suk-Doo can drive, that'll be great.

672
00:49:23,500 --> 00:49:26,680
You didn't tell anyone that
we're going to meet Yun-Shil, right?

673
00:49:26,680 --> 00:49:28,620
Of course not.

674
00:49:29,380 --> 00:49:31,720
Okay, my husband will be home soon.

675
00:49:31,720 --> 00:49:33,590
I'll leave as soon as he gets here.

676
00:49:33,590 --> 00:49:35,410
Bye.

677
00:49:42,630 --> 00:49:44,560
Honey, the kids are waiting.

678
00:49:44,560 --> 00:49:46,340
Where are you?

679
00:49:47,750 --> 00:49:49,620
A workshop?

680
00:49:49,620 --> 00:49:54,740
Mr. Yeom's wife is sick from a cold.

681
00:49:54,740 --> 00:49:56,690
I have to go as his replacement.

682
00:49:57,710 --> 00:49:59,770
Take care of Eun-Suk for me.

683
00:49:59,770 --> 00:50:01,410
He's supposed to do a
camping exercise with his dad.

684
00:50:01,410 --> 00:50:03,320
I can't replace you.

685
00:50:04,370 --> 00:50:06,720
Don't mind other people's business,
and do it right.

686
00:50:06,720 --> 00:50:08,310
That's your job!

687
00:50:08,310 --> 00:50:09,540
My boss is coming! Bye!

688
00:50:16,550 --> 00:50:17,370
Tae-Ran!

689
00:50:17,370 --> 00:50:18,690
Myung-Pil!

690
00:50:24,400 --> 00:50:25,340
Did you wait long?

691
00:50:25,340 --> 00:50:26,540
Nope!

692
00:50:26,540 --> 00:50:29,570
Shall we?

693
00:50:30,610 --> 00:50:32,490
Let's go!

694
00:50:57,690 --> 00:50:58,760
Eun-Suk...

695
00:50:59,560 --> 00:51:03,400
Mom...Dad's not coming?

696
00:51:03,790 --> 00:51:08,420
Why don't we do something
besides camping?

697
00:51:09,680 --> 00:51:13,450
Why don't we make a sand castle
at the beach with Ki-Suk?

698
00:51:13,450 --> 00:51:14,680
Yes!

699
00:51:14,680 --> 00:51:15,470
Okay!

700
00:51:15,470 --> 00:51:17,440
Good? Good!

701
00:51:18,520 --> 00:51:20,750
I'll make a nice sand castle for you.

702
00:51:28,390 --> 00:51:30,630
Hi!

703
00:51:31,730 --> 00:51:33,410
Workshop?

704
00:51:33,410 --> 00:51:37,430
Men who leave during weekends
usually have something to hide.

705
00:51:45,380 --> 00:51:46,470
Hi.

706
00:51:46,530 --> 00:51:47,540
Hi.

707
00:51:47,680 --> 00:51:48,730
Hi.

708
00:51:50,370 --> 00:51:52,340
We have more guests with us.

709
00:52:22,610 --> 00:52:26,460
If Yun-Shil is alive,
then whose corpse was that?

710
00:52:26,460 --> 00:52:27,440
I have a headache.

711
00:52:27,440 --> 00:52:29,300
I hate this!

712
00:52:29,300 --> 00:52:34,750
You didn't get a call from a ghost, right?

713
00:52:36,470 --> 00:52:38,790
I'm glad she's alive.

714
00:52:38,790 --> 00:52:40,720
I'm so glad.

715
00:52:40,720 --> 00:52:43,600
Mom, I want ice cream.

716
00:52:43,600 --> 00:52:45,570
Okay, let's go.

717
00:52:53,300 --> 00:52:54,450
Myung-Pil!

718
00:53:08,650 --> 00:53:10,680
There aren't any guests
named Lee Yun-Shil.

719
00:53:12,710 --> 00:53:15,440
She should be here by now,
but she hasn't even called.

720
00:53:15,440 --> 00:53:17,380
Maybe it was from a wrong number.

721
00:53:18,630 --> 00:53:21,430
Are you sure we're supposed to
see her at the condo coffee shop?

722
00:53:21,690 --> 00:53:23,530
This is the place.

723
00:53:23,540 --> 00:53:27,370
Mom, I want to build a sand castle!

724
00:53:27,370 --> 00:53:28,410
Me too!

725
00:53:29,360 --> 00:53:30,790
Do you want to build one with me?

726
00:53:30,790 --> 00:53:32,640
Yes!

727
00:53:32,640 --> 00:53:33,500
We're at the beach.

728
00:53:33,500 --> 00:53:35,420
Of course they should go see the beach.

729
00:53:35,420 --> 00:53:37,310
I'll be with the kids. Call me.

730
00:53:37,310 --> 00:53:38,310
Let's go.

731
00:54:03,510 --> 00:54:05,300
Did I fall asleep?

732
00:54:05,670 --> 00:54:07,300
Was I asleep for a long time?

733
00:54:08,330 --> 00:54:10,510
Did your arms hurt?

734
00:54:10,510 --> 00:54:13,310
Not at all!

735
00:54:15,380 --> 00:54:21,360
I was happy to see you sleep like a baby.

736
00:54:23,300 --> 00:54:25,670
I must feel relaxed when I'm with you.

737
00:54:25,670 --> 00:54:29,700
I've been taking melatonin
for 3 years because of insomnia.

738
00:54:31,480 --> 00:54:34,730
I haven't slept so soundly in a long time.

739
00:54:36,790 --> 00:54:40,300
Do you want to go to our room?

740
00:54:41,630 --> 00:54:44,360
I'll be your human melatonin.

741
00:54:44,790 --> 00:54:46,350
Sure.

742
00:54:58,700 --> 00:55:02,740
I haven't walked side by side
with a woman in a long time.

743
00:55:03,560 --> 00:55:06,740
Then what about all those times
you walked with Guk-Hee?

744
00:55:06,750 --> 00:55:08,650
What kind of a husband will want
to hold his wife by the shoulder?

745
00:55:08,650 --> 00:55:10,570
We walk front and back.

746
00:55:11,540 --> 00:55:16,640
The other men who are
watching us will say...

747
00:55:16,640 --> 00:55:19,790
'How did he get a woman like her?'

748
00:55:21,350 --> 00:55:23,620
You can say you're a trophy.

749
00:55:23,620 --> 00:55:24,690
Trophy?

750
00:55:24,690 --> 00:55:30,300
Does that mean I'm a trophy wife?

751
00:55:30,790 --> 00:55:33,770
I thought you said
I'm the new good wife?

752
00:55:34,750 --> 00:55:37,500
You'll be a new good wife...

753
00:55:37,500 --> 00:55:39,510
...if someone takes that trophy
and gets a marriage license.

754
00:55:39,510 --> 00:55:42,500
You're such a smooth talker.

755
00:55:46,460 --> 00:55:48,480
Shall we get some beer?

756
00:55:51,560 --> 00:55:55,430
Hey! Hey!

757
00:55:55,430 --> 00:55:57,340
Finish what you're eating first.

758
00:55:57,340 --> 00:55:59,310
I was just in a hurry!

759
00:55:59,710 --> 00:56:02,420
The clerk told me that there's another coffee shop on the 7th floor too.

760
00:56:02,420 --> 00:56:05,350
Maybe that's where Yun-Shil
might be right now.

761
00:56:13,610 --> 00:56:14,740
Go upstairs.

762
00:56:14,740 --> 00:56:17,390
I'll check on the kids first.

763
00:56:17,390 --> 00:56:18,540
Hurry.

764
00:56:24,490 --> 00:56:25,470
Tae-Ran!

765
00:56:25,470 --> 00:56:27,380
Let's get out of here!

766
00:56:27,380 --> 00:56:28,340
Why?

767
00:56:35,690 --> 00:56:38,580
Hurry! Hurry!

768
00:56:44,300 --> 00:56:46,430
Hurry! Get in!

769
00:56:46,430 --> 00:56:48,340
G-G-Guk-Hee is here?

770
00:56:48,340 --> 00:56:50,720
Yes, it was Guk-Hee!

771
00:56:51,690 --> 00:56:53,700
What do we do?

772
00:56:55,620 --> 00:56:58,340
Excuse me. Sorry...

773
00:57:38,730 --> 00:57:39,660
Did you find her?

774
00:57:39,660 --> 00:57:40,680
It's 8th floor.

775
00:57:40,680 --> 00:57:42,420
We need to go up one more floor.

776
00:57:46,750 --> 00:57:49,330
It's okay! It's okay!

777
00:57:49,340 --> 00:57:51,650
She didn't see us!

